                     <interp inst="t18550820-822-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 fishing rod, value 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18550820-name-546" type="victimName">
